headline: Morgan Stanley quants name 7 best stocks on earnings surprise metrics
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley analysts have highlighted seven U.S. companies they believe are best positioned to beat earnings expectations in January, based on what the bank calls its “Earnings Surprise Composite” metric.

headline: Cummins' Quarterly Earnings Preview: What You Need to Know
